      "releaseNotes": "What’s New\n* Smoother login and password reset experience with clearer account messaging\n* Improved performance for shows and events\n* Enhanced support for the new Season Pass experience\n* Improved account validation and input handling\n* Better personalization based on your home park\n* General bug fixes and performance improvements",
