      "currency": "USD",
      "description": "Introducing the all-new Six Flags mobile app! For the first time, all 41 parks are in one app allowing you unparalleled access to our portfolio of world class regional amusement and water parks.\n\nExclusive Access with a Six Flags Account\n\nCreate an account for easy access to all your tickets, passes, memberships and more! Plus, any purchases made with the same email address as your account after creation will automatically show up in your app. Favorite rides for easy access to wait times and get personalized offers for your home park!\n\nNavigate Like a Pro\n\nFinding your way around our parks with ease using the all-new interactive map! You can find ride wait times, figure out what time your favorite show is happening, and use our improved navigation features to find your way to them one step at a time!\n\nOther Features:\n\n- Buy tickets, passes, memberships and more\n- Order food right from the mobile app\n- Mark your parking spot to never forget where you parked again\n- Access your photos taken on your photo pass\n- View your Pass Perks\n- Purchase Single Use Fast Lane for select rides while in park\n- Augmented Reality games (at select amusement parks)\n- Find food meeting different dietary restriction requirements\n\nDownload the latest version of the Six Flags app today and make the most of your next visit to a Six Flags park. Experience fun, convenience, and unforgettable memories, all in the palm of your hand.",
